;者真係好仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你呢D就梗係廢物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費社會資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實交d稅都唔夠政府用係你身上嘅開支，你都係受政府資助嘅廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我由出世到大左病都只係去浸會 由細到大都唔係讀政府資助既學校 美國畢業返黎就開始交稅兼啲咩居屋公屋資格咩都無 請問我用左D咩政府資源呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請問政府用係我身上既開支又係咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係數唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公共資源，例如你行條行人路、搭車條馬路、你去d公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都真係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  條行人路為我而開架? 條馬路為我而造架? D大白象唔係我揀架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實真心 基層無問題 但你窮得黎又玻璃心仲要將件事合理化真係好難抵 同埋我都好好奇 連稅都唔洗交 搵咁少到底你點樣過生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74fd56addbf2e88028c66df8298a55acfd4f930","tid":425832,"uid":71259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:01:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再quote班五毛啦 等佢地無錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c930277750ddf4995d352dece79b4cc02d20a79","tid":425832,"uid":86841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5870fc85301d3a9df4a4847136eb23814e42363b","tid":425832,"uid":140516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blo