係數唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又一件交少少稅以為自己大哂嘅撚樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你係咁話人仇窮 根本係你自己玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得啦知啦你話你唔洗交稅丫嘛好棒棒啊 繼續為五毫字一個 POST 而努力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f794720cb72751ed57b701fe6079dc053d5d16","tid":425832,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c66654dd0f949fef13048d9565a7123c598833ed","tid":425832,"uid":21708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"正！"},{"pid":"6ad7f46ba52d4d37748af1527b544a84a2e742b7","tid":425832,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:05:19.000Z","msg":"勁撚多五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a50d2b55bc9c52a6a2e2969d75e0b658c37f4e3","tid":425832,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">當然你冇咁做</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鍵盤屌&quot;廢老&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係隔離post 屌柒緊你呀<br />\n返去駁我啦 <br />\n<br />\nbtw <br />\nShow Blocked User -&amp;nbsp;JR</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條生癌五毛等錢醫病<br />\n<br />\n佢一定回你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0c6cb43f26e341f20a38a9697a8b36f4587863","tid":425832,"uid":140516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>件&quot;到底乜野名係未用&quot;只係一件狗眼看人低嘅垃圾，讀咁多書只係讀屎片</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLosers gonna lose <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal